instructions.line1: Faylka buugga OCS waa inuu leeyahay dhammaan tiirarrada loo baahan yahay sida loo qeexay OCS.
instructions.line2: Alaabta waxaa lagu qanacsanayaa oo la cusboonaysiinayaa iyadoo la isticmaalayo Nambarka OCS Variant sidii furaha gaarka ah.
instructions.line3: Alaabta cusub waa la gelin doonaa, alaabta jirta waxaa lagu cusboonaysiin doonaa macluumaadka ugu dambeeyay.
instructions.line4: Goobaha qiimaynta iyo tirinta qiimaynta waa la ilaalin doonaa inta lagu jiro cusboonaysiinta.
